description:
The Three Angels’ Messages are the very heart of the Adventist movement. 

These end-time messages found in Revelation 14 drive and guide the evangelistic work of the World Church.

Learn about how the World Church is sharing these messages worldwide and about the variety of resources created to equip church members of all ages to become disciplemakers. 

This, and more, on ANN Weekly. Find other Adventist news stories on our website, adventist.news.
fulltitle: Adventist Church Works to Spread the Three Angels’ Messages
